The '''2006-07 season of the [[Liga I Feminin]]''' was the 17th season of [[Romania]]'s premier women's [[football (soccer)|football]] league. Clujana won the title.<ref>[http://citynews.ro/sport-9/jucatoarele-de-la-cff-clujana-campioane-cu-repetitie-68350 Jucatoarele de la CFF Clujana campioane cu repetitie]</ref><ref>[http://mts.ro/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/MTS-Anuarul-Sportului-2007.pdf Anuarul Sportului 2007 (page 457)]</ref>

