'''PAT Stadium''' ({{Lang-th|แพท สเตเดียม}}) is a [[List of football stadiums in Thailand|stadium]] in the [[Khlong Toei District]] of central [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]].  It is currently used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Port F.C.|Port Football Club]].  The stadium holds approximately 12,000 spectators. PAT Stadium has the motto "This is Khlong Toei - this is the away team's hell".<ref>https://www.fourfourtwo.com/th/features/nrkthiimeyuuen-nnth-ephyrangehyaathiikddansud-nabtangaetyaaymaaaithy</ref><ref>http://www.smmsport.com/m/article.php?a=9287</ref>

