{{Motorsport venue | Name = İzmir Park | Location = [[Pınarbaşı, Bornova]], [[İzmir]], [[Turkey]] | Time = [[UTC]] +2 | Image = | Image_caption = | Events = {{ubl|[[Turkish Formula Three Championship|Formula Three]] |[[Touring car racing|Touring Car]] |[[Turkish motorcycle Grand Prix|Motorcycle Grand Prix]] }} | Length_km = 2.186 | Length_mi = 1.358 | Lap = | Turns = | Record_time = | Layout1 = | Record_driver = | Record_team = | Record_year = }}
'''İzmir Park''', also known as the '''Pınarbaşı Racing Circuit''' or '''İzmir Ülkü Racing Circuit''', is a [[motor sports]] [[race track]] in the [[Pınarbaşı, Bornova|Pınarbaşı]] neighborhood of [[Bornova]] district in [[İzmir]], [[Turkey]]. It was inaugurated in 1997.<ref name="ip">{{cite web |url=http://www.izmirpark.net/detaylar/3/hizmetlerimiz/1008/izmir-ulku-yaris-pisti.aspx |publisher=İzmir Park |title=İzmir Ülkü Yarış Pisti |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-09-21 }}</ref>
İzmir Park stretches over an area of {{convert|245|acre|ha}}. With its {{convert|2.186|km|mi|abbr=on}} length, it is Turkey's second longest race track following [[Istanbul Park]].<ref name="ip"/>
In addition to the asphalt course, which hosts [[auto racing|auto]] and [[motorcycle racing|motorcycle]] and [[karting]] races, there are two more small-sized [[go-kart]] courses and a [[paintball]] playing field inside the main track. The facility includes open and covered stands, a 28-shop paddock, an exhibition area with halls in different sizes, a VIP lounge, training halls and a cafeteria.<ref name="ip"/>
==Major motorsports events== The venue host regularly: * [[Turkish Formula Three Championship]]<ref name="ntv">{{cite news |url=http://arsiv.ntvmsnbc.com/news/154863.asp |newspaper=[[NTV (Turkey)|NTV-MSNBC]] |title=İzmir’de Formula 3 heyecanı |date= |accessdate=2013-09-21 }}</ref> * [[Turkish Touring Car Championship]]<ref name="ntv"/> * [[Turkish Motorcycle Grand Prix]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://arsiv.ntvmsnbc.com/news/106533.asp |newspaper=[[NTV (Turkey)|NTV-MSNBC]] |title=Motosiklet Şampiyonası, İzmir’de |date= |accessdate=2013-09-21 }}</ref> * Turkish Karting Championship<ref>{{cite news |url=http://hurarsiv.hurriyet.com.tr/goster/ShowNew.aspx?id=20398241 |newspaper=[[Hürriyet]] |title=İzmir'de karting heyecanı |date=2012-04-22 |language=Turkish |accessdate=2013-09-21 }}</ref>
